      "_comment": [
        "ROUTING RULES — ordered, FIRST MATCH WINS.",
        "",
        "Each rule has:",
        "  match_fields : Qualys CSV columns to search in. Options: category, title, os, ip, qid",
        "  keywords     : if ANY keyword appears in any match_field, this rule fires (case-insensitive)",
        "",
        "Then set the SDP fields to use for matching tickets.",
        "Pick values from your picklist_reference above.",
        "Leave any field as empty string \"\" to fall back to the 'defaults' value.",
        "Omit a field entirely to also fall back to the 'defaults' value."
      ]
